metadata.name: Fate #1
metadata.description: Project Fate is an anime style PFP project that is story driven. The community will be introduced to a story known as Scars of Fate and will be able to follow along with their Fate NFTs. Following the story, they will be able to experience the different drops and IRL events that will be triggered as the story progresses through our main heroes Luna and Zeroâ€™s journey. Drops may include the chance to receive interchangeable equipment, merch, or even possibly a magical companion for your Fate!
